{"tid":1664211,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"無心 不如 單身","createTime":"2019-10-20T02:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T08:02:44.000Z","uid":91793,"like":87,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0fbb8909fd7552dbc03c621a8c87c85bcf3631eb","tid":1664211,"uid":91793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T02:58:10.000Z","msg":"男朋友消耗曬我對佢既鍾意<br />\n<br />\n有時唔開心 做/講到明想佢氹<br />\n佢都無反應 <br />\n如是者 佢再對我講啲煩惱 已經唔想氹佢<br />\n反正佢都唔理我開唔開心<br />\n<br />\n對我 從來每次九點就返屋企 話攰 話聽日要返工<br />\n對朋友 第二日返工 都可以玩到一兩點都仲未玩夠<br />\n<br />\n星期六日要返工 明明一早講定完咗一齊食飯<br />\n最後無咗件事 同朋友照去玩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明一齊睇完A戲 轉個頭可以問返我 有無睇過呢場戲<br />\n講完既野 完全無記住既 耐咗咩都唔想對佢講啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拍拖真係唔係追求啲野<br />\n但如果你所有野既Priority都排得比我高既時候<br />\n我真係寧願自己一個"},{"pid":"5d4cdd0f2e06cb83d9a1d81e5e0309be5a0c8898","tid":1664211,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:00:50.000Z","msg":"對波幾大"},{"pid":"ab64dd9074683f69cf27c3276d8f53fd7f5f86bc","tid":1664211,"uid":30604,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:03:39.000Z","msg":"佢跟本唔鐘意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a059cf538404e357e111d134b45697a19d957f1","tid":1664211,"uid":173307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:05:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"178df4dd9e90b8faa4566de9cb62d46fc6a7b196","tid":1664211,"uid":91793,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ab64dd9074683f69cf27c3276d8f53fd7f5f86bc","tid":1664211,"uid":30604,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:03:39.000Z","msg":"佢跟本唔鐘意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:11:12.000Z","msg":"呢幾星期 都諗緊呢個問題<br />\n諗緊究竟呢啲係咪鍾意 係咪算拍拖"},{"pid":"0abb4e50c951e1660067551aa4ce92e547a94ce4","tid":1664211,"uid":30604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"178df4dd9e90b8faa4566de9cb62d46fc6a7b196","tid":1664211,"uid":91793,"like":4,